node.text: Set Your ATTENTION ON INTENTION. Bare with us, we never done this before lol. My Mom had the idea of us introducing basic things that have tremendously helped us and people in our circle and your mind is where it all starts, a lot of y’all are probably hip already, but some aren’t and for anyone who’s anxiety runs high, feeling stuck, depressed you might just need to adjust your mindset to get properly started. @seanandersonorg #mentalhealthawarenessmonth

node.text: I sat with Jay Shetty about what I did when I felt hopeless in life, how I handled it, realizing how I was holding myself back at times, books I read that impacted me and helped guide me, wellness n more. Tune into @jayshetty n hear the full podcast.
